summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2379 for the improvement of East Seventy-sixth Street, from Latona Avenue to Eighth Avenue Northeast, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues therein named, all in The City of Seattle, by laying concrete sidewalks and wooden crosswalks; under Ordinance No. 24804, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
